Schiene-Step is a finishing and edge protection profile for ceramic tile and natural stone installations on stairs. The vertical leg of the profile hides the sub-assembly and covers the top of the riser. The profile has an integrated joint spacer which ensures a uniform grout joint between the tile and profile. Schiene-Step is designed for residential applications.Made of satin anodized aluminumAccommodates tiles 5/16 in. thickVertical leg length is 1-1/2 in.For residential stair applicationsPrevents tile edges from chipping